&lt;li&gt;Hands-on maintenance experience on biological research or analytical instruments such as liquid handlers (Hamilton, Tecan, Beckman), plate readers (BioTek, Molecular Devices, BMG), PCR/qPCR systems, automated cell culture platforms, flow cytometers, or imaging systems (ImageXpress, IN Cell)&lt;/li&gt;
